t implant (patients that have had this implant) matching the criteria and no other implants.  The implant data reported is correct but the viewed report may drop patients that should have been reported.   \r\nOpTime - This problem occurs if the region is on SP\"07 with SU E753804 is installed.\r\nRadiant - This problem occurs if the region is on SP\"08.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Code fix installed 4/8/08 E757786, testing passed on 3/26 - recommend closing or verify with IP/Optime\r\nAdhoc or K-package? 11/17:  Radiant affected only in SP08.  Dhea to follow-up with Optime regarding replication, common workflow, communication, remediation, and fix (kpkg vs adhoc-available 11/28).11/18:  Per Darryl Gill-Replication will be attempted in WITS.  Frequent workflow (daily), if public reports are used.  No communication is needed to be sent.  No remediation necessary. Currently, our reports all have Start/End Dates-No issues have been reported. Waiting for Kpkg.\r\n',' Always include the Start Date.  If the Start Date is included, the system will also require an End Date, and the report will be generated correctly.',NULL,' Always include the Start Date.  If the Start Date is included, the system will also require an End Date, and the report will be generated correctly.',NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,141,274,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-11-13 03:45:00','2009-04-29 02:40:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(217,3933718,1,'INPAT',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'Modified sign & held orders may be unexpectedly cancelled.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Med Recon','','',NULL,NULL,'2008-11-13 00:00:00',NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,'Dr. Allan Rogers',NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c75031184, e757784','1126-AP-PR3933718-C75031184-E757784-Spr07Jan19NS.tar.Z--this fix had Hyperspace crash issues. \r\n*********\r\n1212-AP-PR3979615-PR3933718-E757901-C75031225-Spr07Jan19NS.zip\r\n1212-AP-PR3979615-PR3933718-E757901-C75031225-Spr07Jan19NS.tar.Z  ','',NULL,'1900-01-01 00:0